			```
		lineageTag: 471cc296-ebf6-4e5c-9539-6c52ccfc2fb6

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isGeneralNumber":true}

	measure 'Net Rent to Area Ratio ($/sqm)' = ```
			
